# Colors

Our color palette is designed to be accessible and modern.

## Primary Colors

| Name | Hex | Usage |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Primary | `#000000` | Main actions, headers |
| Secondary | `#6e6e73` | Subtext, secondary actions |
| Border | `#e5e5e7` | Dividers, borders |

## Backgrounds

- **White**: `#ffffff` (Main background)
- **Soft Gray**: `#f7f7f8` (Subtle backgrounds, sidebars)